WEBVTT

00:09:29.042 --> 00:09:30.866
The experience of looking up

00:09:31.301 --> 00:09:36.720
and knowing that the sky you're looking at
surrounds every known living thing

00:09:36.744 --> 00:09:38.034
in the universe

00:09:38.058 --> 00:09:39.349
is very profound.

00:09:39.798 --> 00:09:41.270
Think about that for a moment.

00:09:41.294 --> 00:09:45.348
We are the only planet we know of
that has life on it.

00:09:46.392 --> 00:09:49.630
The sky that you see is shared
by every other living thing

00:09:49.654 --> 00:09:51.227
that we know of in existence.

00:09:52.654 --> 00:09:55.631
One of the things
that I really like about my work

00:09:55.655 --> 00:09:59.060
is that it allows me to step back
from my every day

00:09:59.084 --> 00:10:02.292
and to experience the larger context,